Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:25.26,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}摸摸 蹭蹭 ahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.26,0:23:27.03,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:28.80,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}毛茸茸 松抛抛 ahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.57,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}起舞 跃动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:33.94,EDCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2.5}摸摸 蹭蹭 你是最棒的！
